msgid "Scenario V: Return to Undimensioned and Unseen"
msgstr "冒险V：重返无人知晓"

msgid "Remove 4 copies of Brood of Yog-Sothoth from the original scenario and replace them with the 4 new versions of Brood of Yog-Sothoth from the <i>Return to Undimensioned and Unseen</i> encounter set."
msgstr "移除4张原本的犹格·索托斯之子，并以4张<i>重返无人知晓</i>遭遇组中新的犹格·索托斯之子取代。"

msgid ""
"For the duration of this scenario, the following additional rule applies:\n"
"\"If a Brood of Yog-Sothoth would be put into play, it is chosen at random from among the set-aside versions of Brood of Yog-Sothoth.\"\n"
"Attach the Return to Undimensioned and Unseen scenario reference card to the scenario reference card as a reminder."
msgstr ""
"这场冒险期间，请遵守以下额外规则：\n"
"“如果有犹格·索托斯之子将要放置入场，从放在一边的犹格·索托斯之子中随机选择一个版本的犹格·索托斯之子放置入场。”\n"
"将此卡叠加到冒险参考卡，作为提醒。"

msgid "Put 1 random copy of Brood of Yog‐Sothoth into play in Cold Spring Glen and put 1 random copy of Brood of Yog‐Sothoth into play in Blasted Heath. Then, set the final 3 copies of Brood of Yog‐Sothoth aside, out of play."
msgstr "将随机的1张犹格·索托斯之子生成在冷泉幽谷，将随机的1张生成在憎恶荒野，将剩余3张放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid "Put 1 random copy of Brood of Yog‐Sothoth into play in Cold Spring Glen, and set 3 random copies of Brood of Yog‐Sothoth aside, out of play. Then, remove the final copy of Brood of Yog‐Sothoth from the game."
msgstr "将随机的1张犹格·索托斯之子生成在冷泉幽谷，将随机的3张放在一边，位于场外。然后，将最后1张移出游戏。"

msgid "Put 1 random copy of Brood of Yog‐Sothoth into play in Cold Spring Glen, and set 2 random copies of Brood of Yog‐Sothoth aside, out of play. Then, remove the final 2 copies of Brood of Yog‐Sothoth from the game."
msgstr "将随机的1张犹格·索托斯之子生成在冷泉幽谷，将随机的2张放在一边，位于场外。然后，将剩余2张移出游戏。"

msgid "Set 2 random copies of Brood of Yog‐Sothoth aside, out of play. Then, remove the final 3 random copies of Brood of Yog‐Sothoth from the game."
msgstr "将随机的2张犹格·索托斯之子放在一边，位于场外。然后，将剩余3张移出游戏。"
